full_summary: # Tender Announcement: K8F13-230090 ## Commercial-Grade Glassware Washer Supply and Installation ### Issued by the Department of Public Works and Government Services **Contracting Entity Information** Ministry of Public Works and Government Services (Canada) 11 Laurier Street, Phase III, Place du Portage Gatineau, Quebec K1A 0S5 Canada **Project Overview** Environment and Climate Change Canada (ECCC) is seeking a commercial-grade glassware washer to be delivered and installed on site. The proposal should include a detailed breakdown of the supply and installation costs, as well as a timeline for completion. The successful bidder will be required to deliver and install the glassware washer by March 31, 2023. **Technical Specifications** * Unspsc Code: 41103200 (Laboratory washing and cleaning equipment) * Delivery and installation of one stand-alone commercial-grade glassware washer **Procurement Information** * Tender Closing Date: November 23, 2022, 2:00 PM EST * Amendment Number: 4 * Solicitation Number: WS3709631249 * Publication Date: November 2, 2022 * Procurement Method: Competitive - Open bidding * Selection Criteria: Lowest Price **Trade Agreements** The tender is subject to the Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA). **Contact Information** For more information, please contact: Yu, Daphne (SPAC/PSPC) Daphne.Yu@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca **Notice URL** Please access the full Request for Proposal (RFP) and attachments via the SAP Ariba portal at the following URL: [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14519841?extsite=MTQ1MTk4NDFfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14519841?extsite=MTQ1MTk4NDFfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==) Note: This tender has already expired. #TenderExpired Please check with the government agency or contracting entity for further information.
